            text: '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>使用 ***say*** 和 ***tell*** 引述他人说的话</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t**Say** 和 **tell** 意义相近。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/70/33/v/177033/MOB_6.1.3.2.1_1.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>He <strong>said that</strong> she&#39;s very nice but a little shy.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t他说她很善良，但有点腼腆。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/70/34/v/177034/MOB_6.1.3.2.1_2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>He <strong>told me that</strong> she&#39;s very nice but a little shy.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t他告诉我她很善良，但有点腼腆。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t正如您可能注意到的，**tell** 通常与 **me**、**you** 或 **us** 等词搭配使用，而 **say** 无需搭配这些词。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/70/35/v/177035/MOB_6.1.3.2.1_3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 35%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>He <strong>said</strong> he would <strong>tell us</strong> the news next week.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t他说他下周告诉我们消息。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
