            text: '<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 70%;" width="700">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t使用后缀 **-ache** 表示身体某个部位疼痛。该后缀并不适用于所有身体部位，只适用于 **head**、**stomach**、**back** 和 **tooth**。<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/72/23/v/157223/GE_6.2.1.1.2_r5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>He has a <strong>headache</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t他头痛。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/72/24/v/157224/GE_6.2.1.1.2_r6_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I have a <strong>stomachache</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我胃痛。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t使用以下医疗词汇，搭配动词 **be** 或 **feel** 使用。<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/72/25/v/157225/GE_6.2.1.1.2_r7_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 40%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>I<strong>&#39;m dizzy</strong>. I <strong>feel dizzy</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我头晕。我感觉头晕。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/72/26/v/157226/GE_6.2.1.1.2_r8_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 40%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>She<strong>&#39;s nauseous</strong>. She <strong>feels</strong> <strong>nauseous</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t她感觉恶心。她觉得恶心。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3" style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t如果是呕吐，使用动词 **vomiting**。<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/15/72/27/v/157227/GE_6.2.1.1.2_r9_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 40%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>I&#39;ve been <strong>vomiting</strong> for about an hour.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我吐了一个小时左右。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
