            text: '<p>\n\t<strong>现在完成时进行时</strong><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" height="183" style="width: 100%;" width="630">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t用现在完成进行时谈论一种在过去开始一直延续到现在的病症或病。用 **I have been +** 动词\r\n**+ -ing**结构。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/29/34/v/112934/GE_6.2.1.2.1_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I have been vomiting</strong> a lot.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我一直在吐，吐了好多。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/29/35/v/112935/GE_6.2.1.2.1_2_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I have been having</strong> problems sleeping.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我一直都难以睡眠。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t用**for** 增加有关时间的信息。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/29/36/v/112936/GE_6.2.1.2.1_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 40%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>I have been feeling&nbsp;very&nbsp;bad <strong>for</strong> the last two days. </em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t最近两天我一直都感觉不佳。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t医生也可能使用现在完成进行时提问。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/29/37/v/112937/GE_6.2.1.2.1_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>How long <strong>has</strong> this <strong>been going on</strong>?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t这事持续多久了？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/29/33/v/112933/GE_6.2.1.2.1_5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>How long <strong>have</strong> you <strong>been feeling</strong> like this? </em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t你这样的感觉多久了?</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
