            text: '<p>\n\t**While** 和 **when** 描述中断的动作<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t在描述事故时，您通常可以包含两个动作，其中一个动作（**was+ **verb** + ing **）被另一个动作中断。</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="600">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/30/49/v/113049/GE_6.2.4.2.2_2_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I sprained</strong> my ankle <strong>while I was playing</strong> soccer.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我踢足球的时候扭伤了脚踝。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/30/50/v/113050/GE_6.2.4.2.2_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I was walking</strong> on an icy road <strong>when I slipped</strong> and <strong>broke</strong> my leg. </em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t当时我正在结冰的路面上走路，不小心滑倒摔断了腿。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t正如您可能已经注意到的那样，您可以使用**while**而**when**来引入当时正在发生的动作。</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/76/90/v/177690/MOB_6.2.4.2.1_1.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<strong><em>While I was crossing</em></strong><em> the road, a woman fell down.&nbsp;</em></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我过马路时，一个女人摔倒了。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/76/91/v/177691/MOB_6.2.4.2.1_2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<strong><em>When I was driving</em></strong><em> to work, I saw the accident.</em></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我开车去上班时目睹了事故的发生。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t您还可以在**when**来引入第二个动作。</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 100%">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/17/76/92/v/177692/MOB_6.2.4.2.1_3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\tA:<em> What happened?&nbsp;</em></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t发生了什么事？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\tB:<em> I was climbing the ladder <strong>when I slipped</strong>.</em></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我爬楼梯时滑了一跤。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
