            text: "<div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<strong>'who' 引导的关系从句</strong><br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\" width=\"600\">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t用关系从句连接两个句子。关系从句使您的写作和讲话更流利，并帮助您避免重复。关系代词 **who** 用来指人。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>https://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/22/15/v/112215/GE_6.3.3.2.2_1_v2.mp3</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>We have a lot of engineers. The engineers work late.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>https://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/22/14/v/112214/GE_6.3.3.2.2_2_v2.mp3</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>We have a lot of engineers <strong>who</strong> work late.</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t在例子中，主句**We have a lot of engineers** 是一个完整的句子。关系从句**who work late**不是一个完整的句子，故不能独立成句。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- InstanceEndEditable --></div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
